===Pros===
*Cheap and easy to build.
*Can handle up to 2 trains at a time
*Trains don't have to slow down to climb a slope.
*When you make it bigger it is a 8-way roundabout

===Cons===
*Can cause gridlock. 
*Will cause traffic jams. 

[[Category:en/Manual/Train Junctions]]

===Variations===
*When you make it bigger, you can create an 8-way roundabout

